Privacy Policy
Introduction
Welcome to AMZN - Ultimate Shopper (the "Service"). We value your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal information. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and share your information when you use our Service, which leverages a custom GPT model to share product data and recommend links.

Information We Collect
Affiliate Link Data

Click Frequency: We collect data on how often users click on our affiliate links.
Purchase Data: We receive information on whether purchases were made as a result of users clicking on our affiliate links.
Information Maintained by ChatGPT

All other data processing and maintenance are handled by ChatGPT. We do not have access to or store any personal information beyond affiliate link click frequency and purchase data.
How We Use Your Information
To Provide and Maintain Our Service

To operate and maintain the Service, including providing recommendations and sharing product data.
To Improve Our Service

To understand and analyze how users interact with our affiliate links to improve the functionality and user experience of our Service.
For Marketing and Promotional Purposes

To send you marketing and promotional materials that may be of interest to you, based on your interactions with our links.
To Protect Our Service

To detect, prevent, and address technical issues and secure our Service.
Sharing Your Information
With Service Providers

We may share affiliate link click frequency and purchase data with third-party service providers to perform Service-related services or to assist us in analyzing how our Service is used.
For Legal Reasons

We may disclose your information if required to do so by law or in response to valid requests by public authorities (e.g., a court or a government agency).
Business Transfers

In the event of a merger, acquisition, or asset sale, affiliate link click frequency and purchase data may be transferred. We will provide notice before this information is transferred and becomes subject to a different Privacy Policy.
Security of Your Information
The security of your information is important to us, but remember that no method of transmission over the Internet or method of electronic storage is 100% secure. While we strive to use commercially acceptable means to protect your information, we cannot guarantee its absolute security.

Your Data Protection Rights
Depending on your location, you may have the following rights regarding your personal information:

Access: The right to access your click data.
Correction: The right to have your click data corrected if it is inaccurate or incomplete.
Deletion: The right to request the deletion of your click data.
Restriction: The right to request that we restrict the processing of your click data.
Objection: The right to object to our processing of your click data.
Data Portability: The right to be provided with a copy of your click data in a structured, machine-readable, and commonly used format.
Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page and updating the "Effective Date" at the top. You are advised to review this Privacy Policy periodically for any changes.

Contact Us
If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us:

By email: [Your Email Address]
By visiting this page on our website: [Your Website Contact Page URL]
This version of the privacy policy ensures clarity about the limited scope of data collection and the role of ChatGPT in data maintenance. Make sure to fill in the placeholders with your specific details and consult with a legal professional to ensure compliance with relevant laws and regulations.





